{
  "stem": "9908.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in the wintertime, I had a pair of beautiful boots made in the ghetto in Ozorkow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when my mother had to-- she didn't go to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When my mother needed to go for the rations, I left the boots for her to wear then.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I took her shoes to go to work, that she has worn on her feet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the morning, before we left, my sister and myself, we brought water for her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We helped her as much-- [DRINKS] --as we can, that she stays in the house and cook that ration, and you may come home.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In ghetto, we had after the-- the [NON-ENGLISH], they gave us carts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we got food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But when we went in that [NON-ENGLISH], we were dying from hunger.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So for a-- a coin-- a Russian coin, I went to the store.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I got a bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, this was a valuable-- the Russian coins in gold, you know, they are the best in the world.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They have 18 carat gold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So 1/2 of the money was gone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then we start walking to see some bedding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then we sit-- we sit hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Finally, they assigned everybody to go to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My father and my sister were assigned to one of the shops, a tailor shop also.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my-- she worked in my father's group.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Me, I was assigned to a-- [NON-ENGLISH] resort, a shop for ladies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was assigned there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my little brother was a little baby, he was 12 years old, they had-- Rumkowski was a big lover of children, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they had a special shop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brother used to get special food there to eat, better than all of us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Thank God he's-- he's alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
